You hear me?

811
01:42:52.657 --> 01:42:54.181
You're nothing!

812
01:42:56.761 --> 01:42:59.025
You're not Jigsaw, bitch.

813
01:43:02.433 --> 01:43:04.025
You're nothin'!

814
01:43:07.605 --> 01:43:10.369
I'll fuckin' kill you!

815
01:43:10.475 --> 01:43:11.442
No!

816
01:43:11.809 --> 01:43:13.242
That's right.

817
01:43:13.344 --> 01:43:15.642
I'm a murderer.

818
01:43:15.747 --> 01:43:18.272
He took my life from me,

819
01:43:18.382 --> 01:43:20.612
so I just returned
the fuckin' favor.

820
01:43:20.718 --> 01:43:23.619
No, Amanda,
that's what you thought,

821
01:43:23.721 --> 01:43:26.189
but I know different.

822
01:43:26.290 --> 01:43:28.781
You left him for dead, didn't you?

823
01:43:28.893 --> 01:43:30.292
Stop fucking with me.

824
01:43:30.394 --> 01:43:33.625
But I cleaned up
your mistakes.

825
01:43:33.731 --> 01:43:35.995
I forgave you for them.

826
01:43:38.069 --> 01:43:39.866
Let me go! Please!

827
01:43:39.971 --> 01:43:42.963
What you do
is no different than murder.

828
01:43:43.074 --> 01:43:45.907
You torture people.
You watch them die.

829
01:43:46.010 --> 01:43:48.979
But now you're begging me
not to kill this worthless bitch

830
01:43:49.080 --> 01:43:50.809
on the grounds of some game?

831
01:43:50.915 --> 01:43:53.145
You are walking us
toward a precipice, Amanda.

832
01:43:53.251 --> 01:43:54.809
Step back.

833
01:43:54.919 --> 01:43:56.216
It's bullshit.

834
01:43:56.320 --> 01:43:58.811
Nobody changes.

835
01:43:58.923 --> 01:43:59.890
It's all a lie.

836
01:43:59.991 --> 01:44:01.891
If you fail in this, we all fail.

837
01:44:01.993 --> 01:44:04.154
Succeed, and we all succeed.

838
01:44:04.262 --> 01:44:05.889
It's a lie!

839
01:44:11.269 --> 01:44:14.204
I'll tell you,
she hasn't changed,

840
01:44:14.305 --> 01:44:16.603
because nobody fuckin' changes.

841
01:44:18.776 --> 01:44:20.004
Nobody is reborn.

842
01:44:20.111 --> 01:44:21.237
It's all bullshit!

843
01:44:21.345 --> 01:44:23.336
It's all a fuckin' lie!

844
01:44:23.447 --> 01:44:26.245
And I'm just a pawn
in your stupid games.

845
01:44:39.297 --> 01:44:41.288
I don't mean anything to you.

846
01:44:41.399 --> 01:44:44.027
No, you mean everything to me.

847
01:44:44.135 --> 01:44:45.864
Fuck you!

848
01:44:45.970 --> 01:44:47.733
Our fates are linked.

849
01:44:49.207 --> 01:44:51.300
I've tried to help you, Amanda.

850
01:44:51.409 --> 01:44:53.274
So, help me!

851
01:44:53.377 --> 01:44:54.935
Fix me!

852
01:44:56.581 --> 01:44:58.173
Fix me, motherfucker!

853
01:44:59.917 --> 01:45:06.789
I'm standin' right here.

854
01:45:06.891 --> 01:45:08.188
Why is she so important to you?

855
01:45:09.694 --> 01:45:11.753
She's not important to me.

856
01:45:13.598 --> 01:45:15.122
She's important to you.

857
01:45:15.233 --> 01:45:17.463
She's not important to me.

858
01:45:17.568 --> 01:45:21.197
I beg you to reconsider that.

859
01:45:27.011 --> 01:45:28.876
This is your last chance, Amanda.

860
01:45:28.980 --> 01:45:30.242
She's nothing.

861
01:45:47.131 --> 01:45:49.099
Your time's running out.

862
01:45:52.737 --> 01:45:54.398
Now, you think about
what you're doing.

863
01:45:58.376 --> 01:46:00.674
Think about everything
that you've done.

864
01:46:08.219 --> 01:46:11.017
You think about
what you promised me.

865
01:46:11.122 --> 01:46:13.784
Think about our dreams.

866
01:46:13.891 --> 01:46:15.518
Think about tomorrow.

867
01:46:18.529 --> 01:46:19.996
Lynn?

868
01:46:20.097 --> 01:46:21.724
Jeff! Jeff--

869
01:46:22.867 --> 01:46:23.925
Lynn.

870
01:46:26.570 --> 01:46:28.538
Lynn.

871
01:46:28.639 --> 01:46:29.765
- Lynn.
- Jeff.

872
01:46:30.675 --> 01:46:32.336
You just destroyed four lives.

873
01:46:33.611 --> 01:46:35.306
You just murdered Jeff's wife.

874
01:46:55.299 --> 01:46:56.960
Baby.

875
01:46:57.068 --> 01:46:58.433
Amanda.

876
01:47:01.172 --> 01:47:02.139
It's okay.

877
01:47:08.279 --> 01:47:09.439
This was your test...

878
01:47:10.982 --> 01:47:12.574
...your game.

879
01:47:14.785 --> 01:47:16.150
What do I want?

880
01:47:16.253 --> 01:47:17.914
I want to play a game.

881
01:47:20.558 --> 01:47:21.684
You're being tested.

882
01:47:21.792 --> 01:47:22.918
Your will is being tested--

883
01:47:23.027 --> 01:47:24.927
Your will to keep someone alive.

884
01:47:25.029 --> 01:47:25.996
Can you do that?

885
01:47:26.097 --> 01:47:29.897
Can you follow the rules
and grant someone the gift of life?

886
01:47:32.303 --> 01:47:33.964
I was testing you.

887
01:47:34.071 --> 01:47:35.936
I took you in.

888
01:47:36.040 --> 01:47:38.031
You will give everything to me.

889
01:47:38.142 --> 01:47:39.131
Yes.

890
01:47:39.243 --> 01:47:40.301
Every cell in your body.

891
01:47:40.411 --> 01:47:45.405
I selected you for the honor
of carrying on my life's work.

892
01:47:45.516 --> 01:47:47.381
But you didn't.

893
01:47:47.485 --> 01:47:48.452
That's right.

894
01:47:50.421 --> 01:47:51.410
I'm a murderer.

895
01:47:51.522 --> 01:47:52.716
I despise murderers.

896
01:47:52.823 --> 01:47:55.053
You didn't test anyone's will to live.

897
01:47:55.159 --> 01:47:56.524
Game over.

898
01:47:57.828 --> 01:48:00.388
Instead you took away
their only chance.

899
01:48:00.498 --> 01:48:03.126
Your games were unwinnable.

900
01:48:03.234 --> 01:48:04.963
Your subjects merely victims.

901
01:48:05.069 --> 01:48:06.627
You.

902
01:48:07.571 --> 01:48:08.697
There is no turning back.

903
01:48:08.806 --> 01:48:10.797
Do you understand that?

904
01:48:10.908 --> 01:48:16.346
In my desperation,
I decided to give you one last chance.

905
01:48:16.447 --> 01:48:19.245
So I put everything in place.

906
01:48:20.618 --> 01:48:22.347
You chose her 'cause
she's the best, right?

907
01:48:22.453 --> 01:48:24.250
That's one reason I chose her.

908
01:48:24.355 --> 01:48:28.416
You didn't know that Lynn and Jeff
were husband and wife.

909
01:48:28.526 --> 01:48:33.725
I had to keep that from you
for the purposes of my game.

910
01:48:33.831 --> 01:48:36.026
I had to leave out
the ruined marriage,

911
01:48:36.133 --> 01:48:39.296
the cheating wife,

912
01:48:39.403 --> 01:48:44.136
the vengeful husband,
the neglected daughter.

913
01:48:44.241 --> 01:48:49.144
And I let you make
your own choices.

914
01:48:49.246 --> 01:48:52.443
I wanted you to succeed.

915
01:48:52.550 --> 01:48:55.576
Amanda, put it away.

916
01:48:55.686 --> 01:48:57.916
Trust me, even with that gun,

917
01:48:58.022 --> 01:49:01.685
it's Lynn who holds
your life in her hands.

918
01:49:01.792 --> 01:49:03.350
She's not important to me.

919
01:49:03.461 --> 01:49:05.986
I beg you to reconsider that.

920
01:49:06.097 --> 01:49:07.928
Unlock her collar
and let her go.

921
01:49:08.032 --> 01:49:10.364
I said no!

922
01:49:10.468 --> 01:49:12.595
The rules of our game
have been made very clear.

923
01:49:12.703 --> 01:49:15.001
You need to abide by those rules.

924
01:49:17.074 --> 01:49:18.041
You couldn't.

925
01:49:24.381 --> 01:49:26.076
God.

926
01:49:42.066 --> 01:49:43.192
Game over.

927
01:49:55.746 --> 01:49:57.805
You haven't learned anything tonight,
have you?

928
01:49:57.915 --> 01:50:02.113
Your rage and your vengeance
will only hurt the ones you love.

929
01:50:02.219 --> 01:50:05.484
Killing me will only add
to your misery.

930
01:50:05.589 --> 01:50:08.251
It will not bring back your son.

931
01:50:08.359 --> 01:50:10.327
Think of your daughter, Jeff.

932
01:50:10.427 --> 01:50:14.420
She needs you now
more than ever.

933
01:50:14.532 --> 01:50:16.523
You can't kill me, Jeff.

934
01:50:26.177 --> 01:50:28.236
Your wife's dying, Jeff.

935
01:50:28.345 --> 01:50:31.781
Her time's running out.

936
01:50:39.790 --> 01:50:43.521
Jeff, do not miscalculate.

937
01:50:43.627 --> 01:50:45.288
Your fate is in my hands.

938
01:50:45.396 --> 01:50:48.194
Your wife's fate is in my hands.

939
01:50:48.299 --> 01:50:50.529
I love you.

940
01:50:50.634 --> 01:50:52.261
I love you.

941
01:50:56.140 --> 01:50:58.700
I'm taking you home. Okay?

942
01:50:58.809 --> 01:51:02.370
Though you may not
see any threat...

943
01:51:02.479 --> 01:51:04.743
there are threats all around you.

944
01:51:04.848 --> 01:51:07.715
Jeff, if you try to move your wife,
she will die.

945
01:51:07.818 --> 01:51:10.582
I can have an ambulance here
in four minutes.

946
01:51:10.688 --> 01:51:13.384
Would you like to take your wife
out of here tonight?

947
01:51:13.490 --> 01:51:14.980
Would you like
to take her to safety?

948
01:51:15.092 --> 01:51:16.218
Stay.

949
01:51:16.327 --> 01:51:17.851
Stand and face me, Jeff.

950
01:51:17.962 --> 01:51:21.159
- Stay with me, please.
- Right now.

951
01:51:21.265 --> 01:51:24.598
Would you like to get your life back?

952
01:51:24.702 --> 01:51:25.600
Would you, Jeff?

953
01:51:25.703 --> 01:51:27.295
I can make that happen.

954
01:51:29.807 --> 01:51:31.798
Which is it, Jeff?

955
01:51:31.909 --> 01:51:34.104
Come on... yes or no?

956
01:51:34.211 --> 01:51:35.200
Yes.

957
01:51:38.415 --> 01:51:39.677
What do you want?

958
01:51:39.783 --> 01:51:41.375
One final test.

959
01:51:41.485 --> 01:51:43.316
The rules are simple.

960
01:51:43.420 --> 01:51:47.652
Over on that table,
there's a host of vicious implements...

961
01:51:48.993 --> 01:51:52.554
which you can use
to exact your pound of flesh,

962
01:51:52.663 --> 01:51:53.994
to take your vengeance,

963
01:51:54.098 --> 01:51:57.329
to indulge your obsession.

964
01:51:57.434 --> 01:52:02.599
Or you can choose to put
your vengeance aside,

965
01:52:02.706 --> 01:52:04.731
and you can forgive.

966
01:52:06.443 --> 01:52:09.844
You can forgive me for the pain

967
01:52:09.947 --> 01:52:12.643
that I've caused you
and your wife tonight.

968
01:52:14.118 --> 01:52:15.176
Jeff.

969
01:52:15.286 --> 01:52:16.913
Which is it gonna be, Jeff?

970
01:52:21.358 --> 01:52:23.349
Honey, don't do it.

971
01:52:23.460 --> 01:52:25.587
Jeff...

972
01:52:27.464 --> 01:52:29.022
It's up to you.

973
01:52:29.133 --> 01:52:30.191
I need you.

974
01:52:30.301 --> 01:52:33.361
Live or die, Jeff?

975
01:52:33.470 --> 01:52:35.267
Make our choice.

976
01:52:52.856 --> 01:52:53.948
I forgive you.

977
01:53:00.864 --> 01:53:03.230
Jeff...

978
01:53:03.334 --> 01:53:05.928
Jeff. Jeff!

979
01:53:14.945 --> 01:53:16.037
Jeff, no.

980
01:53:30.327 --> 01:53:32.420
I forgive you.

981
01:54:49.775 --> 01:54:51.538
Hello, Jeff.

982
01:54:51.643 --> 01:54:56.103
I made this tape
as an insurance policy, if you will.

983
01:54:59.251 --> 01:55:02.687
And if you're listening to it,
then it's time to collect.

984
01:55:05.257 --> 01:55:08.351
I was your final test of forgiveness.

985
01:55:11.460 --> 01:55:13.155
And if you are listening to this,

986
01:55:13.262 --> 01:55:15.196
then you failed.

987
01:55:16.532 --> 01:55:19.797
Now you must pay the price...

988
01:55:19.902 --> 01:55:22.462
the price for holding onto
all that anger.

989
01:55:22.850 --> 01:55:26.014
The price of driving your
own wife away from you.

990
01:55:26.015 --> 01:55:29.015
The price of living for
nothing but vengeance.

991
01:55:29.016 --> 01:55:31.516
Now I will give you something
to live for.

992
01:55:32.592 --> 01:55:35.322
I told you that
you couldn't kill me, Jeff,

993
01:55:36.228 --> 01:55:38.594
but I didn't tell you why,

994
01:55:39.098 --> 01:55:40.258
and the answer is simple.

995
01:55:40.916 --> 01:55:45.751
I am the person responsible
for the loss of your child.

996
01:55:46.254 --> 01:55:51.851
I am the only person who knows
where your daughter is.

997
01:55:52.610 --> 01:55:55.579
She only has a limited supply of air,

998
01:55:55.680 --> 01:55:56.942
and if you want to get her back,

999
01:55:57.248 --> 01:55:59.273
you'll have to play a game.

